Multi award winning artiste, Adeleke David, popularly known as Davido, graduates from Babcock University, Ilishan- Remo, Ogun State on Sunday. Davido bags a Bachelor of Arts Second Class Upper degree in music. Fulfilling one of the major prerequisite for the completion of his programme, the talented artiste wrote a thesis on the topic: ‘Challenges of Live performance of Afro-pop artists in Nigeria’